hite prevents f5 (for the moment).} Bh3 {which is very distruptive to White's setup. Be careful of g4 from White, trapping the bishop on the edge.} 14. g4 {Going g4 immediately doesn't work out for White.} Ng6 15. Nf5 Nf4 {Black's h3 -bishop lives (and can be reinforced by Ng5 if necessary), while White's f5 -knight is about to be kicked out by g6 .} *

