ause of a nice in-between move tactic:} c6 11. Na3 Bxa3 12. Bxa6 Bb4+ {This is the key. Black removes the bishop from danger with a check, and can then pick of the White bishop on a6 .} 13. Kf2 Nxa6 {With a piece up for Black.} *

