monster on the diagonal, but we're shutting it down quickly.} Qa5 {Black would love a trade of queens.} 14. Qe3 e5 {White avoided the trade, but the Qa5 -move was not useless: The queen helps protect the e5 -square, allowing us to block the a1 - h8 -diagonal for White's bishop. White has decent compensation for a pawn, but no more.} *

